<H2>Research Interests</H2>
<DL>
<DT><!WA5><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
Visual Computing:
Visualization, graphics, vision, imaging, user interfaces.<P>
<DT><!WA6><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
Auditory Computing:
Sound and sonification.<P>
<DT><!WA7><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
HI-I-CUE: Human-Information Interaction via Computers that are
Ubiquitous Everywhere.<P>
<DT><!WA8><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
The Internet and the World-Wide Web.<P>
</DL>

