Section Newsletter.

<DT><!WA41><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
Fountain pens: and other cool stuff <!WA42><a
href="http://www.levenger.com">Levenger</a>.

<DT><!WA43><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
Hot peppers, hot foods: need to check out what's new.

<DT><!WA44><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
Latin music and culture, in particular <!WA45><a
