Gute Fernandez' Brazil Links)</a>. Also, tune in every Monday night,
8:30-10:30 PM to WMBR, 88.1 FM, for <i>Cors&atilde;o Brasileiro,</i>
and every Friday morning, 8:00-11:00 to WFMO, 91.5 FM for more
Brazilian music.

<DT><!WA46><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.uml.edu/icons/Yellow.gif" ALT="o">
The Guitar: Former member of the <!WA47><a
